data.value: This project was created to choose your own car. 1) to add your car to the catalog, click on the second text box and enter your data; 2) To buy a car, register. Enter your login and password. 3) To see the developer click the About button 4) To add a store, enter its name in the first text box. 5) to exit the program, press the exit button
